-- LuxeMatch — seed data
--
-- One demo jeweller "AT Jewellers" with a deterministic UUID so
-- the dev .env.local SHOP_JEWELLER_ID can point at it without provisioning
-- a fresh shop. PIN is "123456" (hash generated by @luxematch/tenant/server
-- hashPin() — DEV ONLY; production installs always use provision-shop).
--
-- Run via supabase CLI:
--   supabase db reset            # applies migrations + seed
--   supabase db push --seed      # apply seed to a remote DB
-- ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

